headline: GoDaddy Inc. to Present at the Barclays Global Technology Conference
summary: GoDaddy Inc. (NYSE: GDDY) Chief Financial Officer Mark McCaffrey will present at the Barclays Global Technology Conference in San Francisco, California on Thursday, Dec. 11, 2025 at 12:15 p.m. ET / 9:15 a.m. PT.

headline: Will GoDaddy's (GDDY) Agent Name Service Launch Redefine Its Role in AI Identity Solutions?
summary: In the past week, GoDaddy launched public access to its Agent Name Service (ANS) API and standards site, offering developers tools to create, verify, and govern cryptographically secure identities for AI agents across protocols. This move highlights GoDaddy's focus on trusted identity solutions and interoperability as the agentic ecosystem evolves rapidly.
